FBIS4-9949 "drlat066_a_94011" FBIS-LAT-93-066 Daily Report 5 Apr 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Official Urges Measures To End Deforestation Official Urges Measures To End Deforestation FL0504180094 Havana Radio Progreso Network in Spanish 1100 GMT 5 Apr 94 FL0504180094 Havana Radio Progreso Network Spanish BFN [Text] At the council of the Ministry of Agriculture's national directorate, Vice Minister of Agriculture (Aguedo Morales) sharply criticized the indiscriminate chopping down of trees and theft and misappropriation of the wood, which are crimes against the nation's patrimony that affect the economy. (Morales) called for strong measures to avoid a repetition of such acts.
